data.description: Home back on market 11/13/23 due to NO FAULT of seller/prior buyer did not clear to close. Seller is offering a one year home warranty. This brick home is in the Morning Woods Subdivision off of Davies Plantation and is in a quiet cove. It boasts features such as a SALT WATER POOL with new pump/liner, secluded primary bedroom, separate shower/tub combo in the primary bathroom, large walk in closet, two fire places, den, bricked in double stacked oven with a counter top stove & screened in patio.
